# Privacy Policy

Effective Date: April 12, 2025

Thank you for using **OhMyCompetitions**, a platform where users can enter fun giveaways and competitions using Pi cryptocurrency. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.

## 1. Information We Collect

We may collect the following information:
- Your name and email address
- Pi Network account details
- IP address and device/browser info
- Information related to your competition entries, gameplay, and win history

## 2. How We Use Your Information

We use your information to:
- Manage your account
- Track entries and award prizes
- Improve our platform and user experience
- Comply with legal obligations
- Prevent fraud and abuse

## 3. Data Sharing

We **do not sell or share** your personal data with third parties except:
- With service providers (e.g., hosting, analytics)
- When required by law or legal process

## 4. Cookies & Tracking

We may use cookies and similar technologies to:
- Keep you logged in
- Understand how users interact with our platform
- Improve our services

## 5. Data Security

We take data protection seriously and use technical and organizational safeguards to protect your information.

## 6. User Rights

You can:
- Request access to your data
- Ask us to delete your account
- Update or correct your information

Please contact us at **support@ohmycompetitions.app** to make a request.

## 7. Children's Privacy

Our app is not intended for users under 18 years old.

